author: GameSpot
description:
The once limited edition Helghast gear is BACK FOR GOOD in the HELLDIVERS 2 x Killzone Legendary Warbond* – deploying to your Destroyer’s Acquisitions Center on December 18th. 

Terrify your enemies with ferocious weapons, special armour, and more – and get this Warbond at no extra cost if you previously purchased any of these items from the Superstore.

*Requires base game, paid purchase of Super Credits, and game progression to unlock. 

#ps5 #ps5games #pcgames #helldivers2
title: Helldivers 2 - Killzone Legendary Warbond Gameplay Trailer

author: GameSpot
description:
Monster Hunter Wilds Free Title Update 4 drops on December 16, 2025! 
 
🌋 Elder Dragon: Gogmazios
🧊 Arch-Tempered Jin Dahaad
⚔️ Expanded Weapon Endgame
🛠️ Performance Improvements & Weapon Buffs
❄️ Festival of Accord: Lumenhymn
 
Gogmazios is coming. Hunters, prepare yourselves!

Monster Hunter Wilds is the next generation of the acclaimed Monster Hunter series.

You are a monster hunter, protecting the balance of the ecosystem and hunting monsters in a world with dynamic, ever-changing environments. Use the resources you gain from hunts to craft ever more powerful weapons and armor in your quest to unravel the mysteries of the new lands.

Experience the most evolved action and improved immersion in the series in Monster Hunter Wilds, available now on PS5, Xbox Series X|S, and PC/Steam!

#monsterhunter #gogmazios #videogames
title: Monster Hunter Wilds - Free Title Update 4 Overview Trailer
